<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Art Room</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0a0a2a;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .image-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .image-grid img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .image-grid img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ART ROOM</h1>
        <div class="image-grid">
            <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/009/829/074/non_2x/astronaut-space-explorer-mascot-logo-vector.jpg" alt="Space Explorer Logo">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Space Explorer Logo">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Nebula">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQmT82LtRGExV5Heg3W8zLVCyrG4PWqr0eUhg&s" alt="Solar System">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR20dmX-09r4ZMVAcP5DuHN3uIgWPfT4fETEw&s" alt="Galaxy">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Celestial Bodies">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQeWEu1AYFxZyzs2HGi1XVCTqWwJUxxc9QBgg&s" alt="Space View">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSqwv51-7HYIFJL-hVfMwzFEEqY2SddIkk4Lw&s" alt="Space Scene">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
